  "hadithShawwalTitle": "Six Days of Shawwal",
  "hadithShawwalBody": "Whoever fasts Ramadan and follows it with six days of Shawwal, it will be as if he fasted for a lifetime.",
  "hadithEidDaysTitle": "Eid Days",
  "hadithEidDaysBody": "The Prophet (peace be upon him) forbade fasting on the day of Eid al-Fitr and the day of Eid al-Adha.",
